home.description:
A free and open-source Nuxt.js project starter template with essential features for modern web development. 
Includes mobile and dark mode support, multilingual setup, and Nuxt Content for easy documentation creation.
home.nuxt: Nuxt is an open source framework that makes web development intuitive and powerful.Create performant and production-grade full-stack web apps and websites with confidence.
home.nuxtUi: Nuxt UI is a module that provides a set of Vue components and composables built with Tailwind CSS and Headless UI to help you build beautiful and accessible user interfaces.
home.nuxtContent: Nuxt Content reads the content/ directory in your project, parses .md, .yml, .csv and .json files to create a powerful data layer for your application.
home.vue: An approachable, performant and versatile framework for building web user interfaces.
home.ts: TypeScript is a strongly typed programming language that builds on JavaScript, giving you better tooling at any scale.
home.tailwindcss: Tailwind CSS is a utility-first CSS framework for rapidly building modern websites without ever leaving your HTML.
home.i18n: Vue I18n is internationalization plugin for Vue.js.
home.pinia: The Vue Store that you will enjoy using
